   --  |  |    |                                                            |
   --  |  |    +--> Process_Guaranteed_ABE_Instantiation                    |
   --  |  |                                                                 |
   --  +- | ----------------------------------------------------------------+
   --     |
   --     |
   --     +--> SPARK_Scenarios
