   --     +--> Top_Level_Scenarios
   --     |    +-----------+-----------+ .. +-----------+
   --     |    | Scenario1 | Scenario2 | .. | ScenarioN |
   --     |    +-----------+-----------+ .. +-----------+
   --     |
