   --  |  +--> Process_Conditional_ABE <---------------------------+        |
   --  |       |                                                   |        |
   --  |       +--> Process_Conditional_ABE_Access    Is_Suitable_Scenario  |
   --  |       |                                                   ^        |
   --  |       +--> Process_Conditional_ABE_Activation             |        |
