   --  |       |    +-----------------------------+                |        |
   --  |       |                                  |                |        |
   --  |       +--> Process_Conditional_ABE_Call  +--------> Traverse_Body  |
   --  |       |    |                             |                         |
   --  |       |    +-----------------------------+                         |
   --  |       |                                                            |
   --  |       +--> Process_Conditional_ABE_Instantiation                   |
   --  |       |                                                            |
